text:
I just want to say how happy I am with the service Chris (T25) provided for me (here in Elanora) he did a 40km service on my Mazda and he did a fabulous job. He is a pleasure to talk to and I will definitely be recommending Lube Mobile to friends and family, in particular Chris!.
Susanna. T
